{"tid":2021223,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「九西」有候選人獲文匯認證","createTime":"2020-05-17T15:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T12:32:24.000Z","uid":42007,"like":33,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"03b42cdffff6ed26419bdf0672e862535fb10247","tid":2021223,"uid":42007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:04:55.000Z","msg":"話說，有意參選九西嘅劉澤鋒擺街站，點知受文匯攻擊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6eccca7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6eccca7.png&h=00d1e4b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除咗「認證」佢係港獨派之外，仲寸人「講到咁熱鬧，篇帖文得返寥寥回應，好似市民都用行動表達緊，撐「攬炒」，你慳啲啦。」<br />\n唔知全能嘅連登仔，成日話唔知有邊個可以投，又會唔會上佢facebook支持吓佢，like吓佢個page呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下面係文匯link，唔需要按入去。<br />\n【網議政事】稱「攬炒」主流乏人回 劉澤鋒自打嘴巴<br />\n<a href=\"http://paper.wenweipo.com/2020/05/14/HK2005140040.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.wenweipo.com%2F2020%2F05%2F14%2FHK2005140040.htm&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCfcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=a5113772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://paper.wenweipo.com/2020/05/14/HK2005140040.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2082b284c8601fa862878d4a724ba008e2da2854","tid":2021223,"uid":42007,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:06:11.000Z","msg":"樓主好靚仔"},{"pid":"7c1d6498f363245ee404d1f4fa99d60c843feac1","tid":2021223,"uid":42007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:07:31.000Z","msg":"留名等睇冇人理樓主"},{"pid":"9851241aff9ef8738ff7942903e7cf776541fd74","tid":2021223,"uid":42007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:08:06.000Z","msg":"樓主，多謝你的資訊"},{"pid":"65d6bd510d7bdacc184553c7c7f02a462cfafe8e","tid":2021223,"uid":42007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:08:32.000Z","msg":"多謝樓主"},{"pid":"e50bdc98469675dd113216b533cbf753fd1d7d0a","tid":2021223,"uid":42007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:22:39.000Z","msg":"咁都有負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa